e in the arts (literature, drama, film, music).  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aDialoganalyse. 4aKonferenz. 4aLinguistik. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aAirenti, Gabriella, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAraujo Carreira, Maria Helena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaggio, Mario, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBak, Yong-Ik, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBazzanella, Carla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBearth, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBondi Paganelli, Marina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonfantini, Massimo A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoutet, Dominique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChristmann, Ursula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCigada, Sara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCmejrková, Svetla, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aContento, Silvana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDascal, Marcelo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDavidová, Dana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDelefosse, J. -M. Odéric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDuBartell, Deborah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDuszak, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFavretti, Rema Rossini, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/